ComicInfo.Summary: Francine tries to sneak out of the apartment, not knowing how to deal with Katchoo and the kiss they nearly shared the previous night. She also finds out Rachael and Chuck are an item. Katchoo goes to find David and finds his sparse apartment vacated but with evidence of his feelings for her. Rachael shows what a ruthless manipulator she is in all aspects of her life much to Chuck and Francine's discomfort.
